{"title":"祝福夏天（二首）","authors":["聂作平"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":6,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聂作平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛙声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在夏天的背面，唱起来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少蛙声一直在寻找"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那些远离家园的亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地复苏，花蕾吐绽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天总要通过这群"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝福者的金嗓子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们和田野致词"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天，蛙声集合了劳动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动，集合了花朵粮食"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有夕阳和炊烟渐收时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村庄羞涩如水的梦寐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷仓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心平气和的年代，夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从一阵鸟啼开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收获我们磨好镰刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备筑好心胸豁达的谷仓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望丰收提早报到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水和老茧争诵传福音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高大、结实、向阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就像父亲在风雨中挺直脊梁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷仓在盆地行走的岁月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见灯火与村庄之间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人寿年长丰衣足食"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}